Privacy Policy The Idea Investment Group (IIG) App is to improve administrative process better services.
IIG app, we prioritize the protection of the privacy and security of our register member, including you. We know and fully understand and respect the importance of data privacy and security on the Internet.
We expect you are informed and secured when it comes to our handling and usage of your information. This notice therefore explains:
• what information we collect when you’re using IIG app, or when you’re communicating with us;
• why we collect that information;
• how we may then use that information;
• how we share that information;
• how long we keep your information, and how we protect it whilst we have it;
• what we won’t do with your information;
• and what choice and options you have to control your information.


Collection of Personal Information
IIG will never sell, share or trade register’s personal information collected online with third parties. Personal information collected from register form will only be disclosed within IIG database server and use it for paper printing and let you sign for only. When you register a IIG account, the personal information we collect may include your:
• Name
• Phone
• Address


Disclosure of Personal Information
We will not share your information with any other organization other than our data collection and purpose for which you have authorized. If you believe that your privacy has been breached by IIG please contact our IT Department and we will try to resolve the issue.


Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may change this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make significant changes in the way we treat your personal information, or to the Privacy Policy, we will make that clear on the IIG website or Services, or by some other forms of communication, so that you are able to review the changes before you continue to use IIG App.
However, it is your responsibility to review this policy from time to time to get yourself update. This page was last updated on 14th October 2022.
